{
  "stem": "8679.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every imaginable kind of workshop, whatever's demanded in the state.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Clothing, furniture, [? material ?], you know, [INAUDIBLE] everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A bakery, a butcher-- I don't know about the butcher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We never had meat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything was done in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Chaim Rumkowski had this office in a certain place in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he couldn't leave either, but a German administrator-- his name was Hans-- H-A-N-S-- Biebow-- B-I-E-B-O-W.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He came in with his helpers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All-- it's all Germans, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he demanded-- Germany sent in raw products, and we worked 12 hours a day on a starvation diet, if I might let you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was one loaf of bread for a week, which sounds a lot today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't eat a loaf of bread a week, but it wasn't much more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the beginning, we had potatoes, and it was a very highly-desired food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It shortly disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then we got, instead of potatoes, potato peels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were given out on doctor's prescription in the beginning, then it was taken off completely.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had a lot of red beets and kohlrabi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's a vegetable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's not the slightest [INAUDIBLE] of nourishment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And these workshops supplied [? the ?] soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we came home and had another soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember my mother making-- we had-- we didn't need ration cards to buy caraway seeds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My mother's favorite soup was caraway seeds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It gave it a color and a smell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And red beets were swimming around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I ate my kohlrabi raw, and we had some brown sugar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that was my meat, my vegetable, my dessert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were hungry when we got up in the morning, and I can assure you, we were hungry when we go-- went to bed.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
